description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation with Mooji — The Call From Within' from the channel Moojiji.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Wherever we may be, whatever our outward circumstance, this is an invitation to be fully here, in the presence of God. Simple, deep and profound, in this meditation Moojibaba guides us into the direct recognition of stillness, which is revealed as our original and essential nature.

"Let go and experience emptiness. Be the emptiness experiencing emptiness."

Monte Sahaja, Portugal
19 April 2024
~
